Package: wows-splash-cli
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         libwows-splash0 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Command-line parser for World of Warships splash files
 Command-line interface for parsing the .splash file format used in
 World of Warships, which describes ship hitbox geometry.

Package: libwows-splash0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Library for parsing World of Warships splash files
 Shared library for parsing World of Warships .splash files.
 This package contains the runtime library.

Package: libwows-splash-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         libwows-splash0 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Development files for libwows-splash
 Development files for the wows-splash library, including header files
 needed for developing applications that use wows-splash.
